## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ocrelizumab Ocrevus 2017** = first FDA anti-CD20 MS — RRMS + PPMS 동시 적응증. PPMS 처음으로 FDA 승인 약물. CD20+ B cell depletion 이 MS pathogenesis B-cell axis 확립. quantum-VQE 의 Fab CD20 pocket scaffold fit.
2. **siponimod Mayzent 2019** = first FDA SPMS active. fingolimod 의 S1P1/5 selective 후속 — S1P3 회피로 cardiac/macular 부작용 감소. quantum-VQE 의 GPCR S1P pocket selectivity 직접 fit.
3. **BTKi class 4종 (evobrutinib + tolebrutinib + remibrutinib + fenebrutinib) 2024 Phase 3** = BBB-cross + B cell + microglia 양면 표적 — MS 의 첫 BTKi class 가 임상 paradigm shift 가능. quantum-VQE 의 BTK kinase domain pocket leverage.
4. **NMOSD 4종 (eculizumab 2019 + inebilizumab 2020 + satralizumab 2020 + ravulizumab 2024)** = AQP4+ NMOSD 가 5년 새 4종 FDA 승인 — orphan disease paradigm shift. MS 와 distinct mechanism (C5 + CD19 + IL-6R + long-half-life C5). cross-myasthenia_specific 와 mechanism 동일.
5. **fumarate 3 generation (DMF 2013 + diroximel 2019 + monomethyl 2020)** = Nrf2 + GSH antioxidant — same active metabolite, GI tolerability iterative 개선. quantum-VQE 의 covalent Nrf2-Keap1 결합.
6. **anti-CD20 expansion 3종 (ocrelizumab 2017 + ofatumumab 2020 + ublituximab 2022)** = MS B-cell depletion 이 mainstream. ofatumumab SC 자가-administered, ublituximab 짧은 infusion — patient convenience iterative.
7. **natalizumab 2004 + PML/JCV** = α4β1 integrin first-in-class — efficacy 강력하지만 JCV reactivation PML 위험. JCV antibody index 가 risk stratification → patient-selected 적응증 evolution.
8. **alemtuzumab Lemtrada 2014** = anti-CD52 pulse — autoimmune secondary (Graves + ITP + GBM) 후속 위험. cross-bone_marrow_failure CD52 PNH alternative.
9. **MOGAD (MOG-IgG)** = 2020+ separate disease entity — NMOSD 와 distinct, MS 와 distinct. FDA-approved DMD 없음 (rituximab off-label + IVIg + steroids). research gap.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, MS + NMOSD 임상 의미 한정.

